N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4813.3 - How application is processed

State Regulations

The application to amend a license together with
appropriate schedules shall be filed in triplicate and processed in the same
manner as provided in this Chapter for original applications. Notes
